Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.44,0:00:17.38,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}微风轻吻着脸庞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.68,0:00:20.81,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}用着一种怀念的温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.05,0:00:29.48,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}吹干流下的泪珠轻拂而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.69,0:00:36.10,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}不管是谁 对未来都着着一股不安的期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.30,0:00:48.73,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}就朝着明天大步迈进吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.11,0:00:51.28,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}GUNPARADE MARCH
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.28,0:00:57.62,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}总有一天会觉醒的 真实心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.85,0:01:03.85,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}现在就伸出双手去感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.89,0:01:14.13,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}在这开始变化的世界 立刻前往探寻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.24,0:01:20.81,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}牵系着你的手绝不再分离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.81,0:01:24.18,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}因为有你在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.21,0:01:28.05,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}所以一定找寻的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.69,0:01:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月了 春天到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.69,0:01:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望望美我最喜欢春天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.46,0:01:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天会开好多花 太阳公公也好暖和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.71,0:01:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校也焕然一新
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.37,0:01:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多新人进来 还有好多新的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.72,0:02:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.06,0:02:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望望美我最喜欢春天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.16,0:02:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望望美 快捡球！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.56,0:02:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球啦 在你后面了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.03,0:02:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「第八话  四月的她」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.25,0:02:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来、我来～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.25,0:02:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.36,0:02:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.53,0:02:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田边 你没事吧 田边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.96,0:02:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 她完全失去意识了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.90,0:02:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把她带到保健室如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.08,0:03:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.62,0:03:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没怎么样真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.16,0:03:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过看来休养一下比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.46,0:03:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉让各位担心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.33,0:03:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 话说回来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.30,0:03:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是怎么来到这里的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.94,0:03:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.31,0:03:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.64,0:03:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有看到田边的表情吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.51,0:03:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 速水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.82,0:03:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连耳根都红了 好可爱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.62,0:03:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她似乎不会排斥呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.62,0:03:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好像其实对速水…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.93,0:03:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要再说了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.19,0:03:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.33,0:03:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.53,0:04:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大家都怪怪的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.24,0:04:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.21,0:04:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是田边也有权力选对象啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.51,0:04:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次不错喔 速水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.45,0:04:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然看到你受欢迎的一面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.05,0:04:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘记写作业了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.63,0:04:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑户口…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.37,0:04:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有作业能给男人抄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.94,0:04:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水 作业借我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.74,0:04:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给速水学长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.88,0:04:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一年四班的新井木勇美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.15,0:04:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事一定要告诉学长 所以才写了这封信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.95,0:04:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我烦恼了很久 不过一直这样子也没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.96,0:05:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想下定决心说清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.66,0:05:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 我从以前就对学长…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.83,0:05:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水 这应该是情书吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.17,0:05:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年四班 座号三号 新井木勇美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.41,0:05:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八月四号出生 狮子座A型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.55,0:05:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在今年的新生中 长相名列前茅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.35,0:05:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然已经调查好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.19,0:05:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个勇美怎么会对你？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.92,0:05:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水收到情书耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.99,0:05:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.19,0:05:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－他们的精神年龄几岁啊\N-别这样 快还我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.56,0:05:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说别这样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.07,0:05:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系 给我看啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们玩够了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.51,0:05:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛生气啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.65,0:05:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 让我们看啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.21,0:05:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.45,0:05:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-快把他压住\N-总之借我们看啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全被拿来炒作了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.82,0:06:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟这可是个话题啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.59,0:06:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那真的是情书吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.96,0:06:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.73,0:06:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会有人恶作剧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.33,0:06:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.03,0:06:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒是有可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.54,0:06:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小舞 你已经吃饱了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.24,0:06:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.49,0:06:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您看了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.49,0:06:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是新井木？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.12,0:06:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.70,0:06:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正中直球呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.71,0:06:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.58,0:07:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.52,0:07:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-勇美好厉害\N-好棒的告白呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.97,0:07:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.11,0:07:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.55,0:07:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的模拟训练是4A吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.19,0:07:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.69,0:07:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.70,0:07:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要交往还是要拒绝？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.43,0:07:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多也该讲明白了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.77,0:07:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.57,0:07:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么这个样子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.64,0:08:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.94,0:08:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说 就是没有交往的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.35,0:08:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.28,0:08:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果不明讲的话 对她而言也是很可怜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.59,0:08:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.86,0:08:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.46,0:08:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法 我就传授给他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.96,0:08:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不能外传！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.60,0:08:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个恋爱高手所创的\N「不伤害对方并拒绝」的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.87,0:08:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这种方法吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.17,0:08:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧 听清楚啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.84,0:08:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈咪～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.95,0:08:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈咪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.68,0:08:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法当面拒绝 就得让她讨厌你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.95,0:08:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把自己的母亲称作妈咪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.86,0:08:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有恋母情节 绝对会被讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.96,0:08:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这破坏力大概超过PBE了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.56,0:08:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是幻兽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.10,0:08:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外还有别的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.46,0:08:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如嘴里碎碎念 假装很危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.87,0:09:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说自己的兴趣是编蕾丝等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.81,0:09:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.11,0:09:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有其他喜欢的女生 应该是最好的理由了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这毕竟是王道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.72,0:09:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.42,0:09:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-击破数8\N-命中率55%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.52,0:09:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中弹数0
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.53,0:10:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这阵子状况一直不太好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.26,0:10:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是因为那个原因吗 最近速水身边似乎很热闹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.13,0:10:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我要说的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.54,0:10:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村的数值下降了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.54,0:10:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.42,0:10:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水学长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.29,0:10:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.42,0:10:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新井木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请叫我勇美吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.93,0:10:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 就算你这么说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水学长真会欺负人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.93,0:10:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺负？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.97,0:10:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过学长 这礼拜天有空吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.27,0:10:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.57,0:10:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去看电影呢 我有两张票喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.84,0:10:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.35,0:10:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看完电影之后 再去喝个茶吃晚饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到吃完饭之后…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.95,0:11:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我…其实…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.82,0:11:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你有其他喜欢的人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.96,0:11:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁 学长喜欢的是谁呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.97,0:11:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.50,0:11:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.87,0:11:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不、那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.87,0:11:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这种让人误解的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会跟这种人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.48,0:11:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.11,0:11:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长不会喜欢那种人对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水那家伙结果如何啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.71,0:11:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会是今天吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.64,0:11:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像他那种人啊 一定是不好意思到底的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.98,0:11:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不一定喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.15,0:12:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫新井木的女孩很积极喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.28,0:12:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒速水变成被动了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.42,0:12:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 新井木不要这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.52,0:12:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 要叫我勇美喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.23,0:12:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有一点我不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.90,0:12:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是拒绝约会过一次吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.80,0:12:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定他真的有其他喜欢的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.40,0:12:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 听到芝村时他还脸红…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.41,0:12:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么傻话 哪有这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.28,0:12:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水他本人也否认啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.32,0:12:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小舞 你还要再洗一次吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.19,0:12:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我说速水跟芝村啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.19,0:12:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两人之间或许有什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.33,0:12:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个姊姊我就不知道啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.03,0:12:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别来了 你一定什么都知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.94,0:13:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吝啬 跟我们讲啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.61,0:13:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事放着不管 迟早会知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.98,0:13:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.58,0:13:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在去年的圣诞夜 速水跟芝村他们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.32,0:13:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是两个人独处对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.22,0:13:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这么说来\N-那时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.73,0:13:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到圣诞夜时一对男女该做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.23,0:13:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哪位知道会是什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.75,0:13:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没想过你是累赘 我也不会丢下你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.25,0:13:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？你没去约会？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.26,0:13:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.26,0:13:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起、对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.39,0:13:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我道歉有什么用啊 笨蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.90,0:13:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼！恶魔！没骨气！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.28,0:14:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全上垒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.56,0:14:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 比赛要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.53,0:14:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以突然变冷淡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.80,0:14:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫新井木是吧 之前关系不是有所进展了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.64,0:14:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.94,0:14:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我后来没有去约会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.18,0:14:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.54,0:14:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问为什么我也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.65,0:14:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是出门了吗 不然你在外面作什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.55,0:14:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.82,0:14:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一个人在街上晃 然后吃个饭 到书店去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.19,0:14:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不长进的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.69,0:14:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为这样 我才放不下心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.03,0:15:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.34,0:15:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该要画线啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.22,0:15:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的比赛要开始啰 快点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.62,0:15:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.42,0:15:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.00,0:15:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.37,0:15:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吗 速水学长 你怎么参加比赛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.74,0:15:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒已经好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.37,0:15:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不、那个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.28,0:15:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好担心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.75,0:15:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上你打电话来时\N不但一直咳嗽 声音也沙哑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.75,0:15:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-听说烧到40度 还拉肚子\N-感冒啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.89,0:16:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来至少还是有解释呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.39,0:16:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没有问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.23,0:16:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.90,0:16:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打者就位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.77,0:16:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-为什么班长\N-为什么我们就不能上场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.54,0:16:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了公平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.31,0:16:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.05,0:16:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来、我来～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.55,0:16:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.92,0:16:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新井木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.03,0:16:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-勇美\N-勇美没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.43,0:16:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新井木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.83,0:16:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把她…带到保健室如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.08,0:16:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小志 不赶快的话 她会很痛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.62,0:17:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你还好吧\N-勇美…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.68,0:17:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水学长…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.99,0:17:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急广播、紧急广播
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.16,0:17:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5121部队请尽速准备出击 再次广播
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.69,0:17:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须走了\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}5121部队请尽速准备出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.57,0:17:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实真的很痛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.54,0:17:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.17,0:17:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.24,0:18:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有接吻吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.24,0:18:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦 你们真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.48,0:18:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么嘛\N-真是无聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.35,0:18:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不无聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.82,0:18:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水学长是要出击 这可是要赌命的崇高使命呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.42,0:18:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到这里啊勇美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.72,0:18:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 至今都没有说那个人到底哪里好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.46,0:18:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.06,0:18:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你中学就很崇拜驾驶员 会看新闻 调查各个部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.07,0:18:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为什么会是他啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.20,0:18:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员不是还有很多吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.47,0:18:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我就觉得濑户口学长不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.74,0:18:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是速水学长就不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.18,0:18:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们根本就不知道他的真实一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.75,0:18:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水厚志 战士中的战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.19,0:18:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极限之下的正确判断力 还有不畏惧死亡的勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.89,0:18:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重点是他无人能比的战斗力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.99,0:18:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才是理想中的驾驶员呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次搞得真是不得了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.51,0:19:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要帮写领料单的人想想嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.48,0:19:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了呢 速水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.98,0:19:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.51,0:19:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村 你也不像平常的你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.02,0:19:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 幸好两人都没受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.39,0:19:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次你可得帮忙修理喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.32,0:19:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.63,0:19:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长、速水学长！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.27,0:19:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长你没事吧 有没有受伤？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.17,0:19:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.04,0:19:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.57,0:19:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有什么我能做的 我想要帮学长的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.24,0:19:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长 我…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.15,0:19:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.25,0:19:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.79,0:19:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道何时会被召集 每次出动也不一定能平安回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.69,0:19:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我没办法跟你好好交往的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.33,0:20:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢学长 我一直都很崇拜学长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在去年的菊池县攻防战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.30,0:20:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道学长在那场激战担任PBE的活跃事迹之后…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.21,0:20:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在菊池战并不是负责PBE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.11,0:20:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.21,0:20:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责菊池战PBE的 记得是8331部队呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.58,0:20:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 那边的三号机的确也是双人座机型的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.06,0:20:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新井木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.06,0:20:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我认错人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.80,0:20:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今发生的事情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.33,0:20:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你全部忘记吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.34,0:20:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今发生的事情 请你全部忘记吧～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.84,0:20:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来、原来她搞错人啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.48,0:20:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是杰作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.12,0:20:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小舞在笑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.89,0:21:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好像很高兴的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.16,0:21:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.90,0:21:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望望美我最喜欢春天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.16,0:21:47.56,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}最重要的心情 总是过于接近无法传达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.14,0:21:59.91,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}擦肩而过时的悲伤 在我的内心紧紧纠结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.21,0:22:05.81,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}雨过天睛 光珠般的雨滴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.42,0:22:11.88,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}我将其收集起来 藉以思念你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.43,0:22:19.39,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}没人知道我将前往何处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.70,0:22:25.66,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}只有明日的风描绘着我的轨迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.17,0:22:31.58,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}随着时代变动的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.91,0:22:37.71,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}即使迷失在困惑里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.95,0:22:44.29,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}也要抱紧这相遇的奇迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.46,0:22:54.27,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}走吧 一同前去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.47,0:22:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.54,0:23:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦 平常不都是望望美负责吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.48,0:23:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 要说什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.38,0:23:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最不擅长这个了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.75,0:23:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话的高机动…
